                          Choosing a weapon
                          ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  You choose a weapon by clicking on it in the scrolling list named
'Available Weapons'. When you do this, the weapons name will appear in
the 'Chosen Weapons' box, which is the weapons which will be shown on
