@TOC "Abilities"
@Prev "Abilities_Fighting"
@Next "Abilities_Spell"

  Allows you to choose which proficiencies your character shall have.
You will notice that there are different colors on the lines in the
scrolling list of proficiencies. These colours relate to how many
slots the proficiency takes in the manner descriped on screen.

o Free proficiencies are just that, Free. They are available to your
  character at no cost in proficiency slots.

o Normal proficiencies are those that your character can learn
  normally, at the normal cost.

o Special proficiencies are those proficiencies that your character
