@Node "Settings_Character_Slow"
@Title "Settings/Options/This character/Slow, unlimited advancement"
@TOC "Settings_Character"
@Prev "Settings_Character_AllAllowed"
@Next "Settings_Character_Race"

  This optional rule from DMG allows multiclassed demihumans to
advance above their normal maximum level limit. The slow advancement
