@Node "Settings_Character_AllWarriors"
@Title "Settings/Options/This character/All warriors can specialize"
@TOC "Settings_Character"
@Prev "Settings_Character_WeaponSpec"
@Next "Settings_Character_Multiple"

  This is the rule from the 'The Complete Fighter's Handbook', that
allows all warriors to specialize (an error ???). This is implemented
by allowing all classes, which have the 'Weapon specialization' and
'Max one weapon specialization' options under 'Design, Class, Options'
