@Node "Settings_Character_Int13"
@Title "Settings/Options/This character/Int 13 for Thought and Numbers"
@TOC "Settings_Character"
@Prev "Settings_Character_Int"
@Next "Settings_Character_MaximumHp"

  A recomended rule from the Tome of Magic. It requires the character
to have 13 in intelligence before he/she can cast spells from the
